question: PTID
resonse_labels: Follow your Center’s Patient ID scheme; use same ID as in MDS, if subject is enrolled in MDS.

question: ADC name
resonse_labels: Use your Center ID. Valid codes are available here: https://naccdata.org/center-ids

question: ADC Visit Number
resonse_labels: Can be determined by Center. The Center may use its existing visit number scheme. It is not required to start with 1.
